A fatal head-on collision occurred on Station Road, Eastbury, Phoenix a short while ago. One person who is believed to be the mum is entrapped and deceased and two children aged 13 and 16 are critically injured in the collision. The injured are being attended to by KZN VIP paramedics. All services are on scene. Motorists are urged to stay away from the accident scene. This is a developing story and updates will follow as new information is available.